data.description: This is the only 4bd, 3.5ba home available priced below $400,000 in the neighborhood. Not only does this home offer a fabulous floor plan with guest suite on the main level it is also fabulously located on a greenbelt, offering tons of privacy, and is within a block to the pool and playground. The island kitchen offers tons of cabinets incl. gas cooking and double ovens. The primary bedroom is huge and provides double walk in closets and a spa like bath. The large game room invites for gatherings, the laundry room is upstairs so no carrying laundry baskets downstairs. This is an incredible price and with a little TLC it could be your dream home. Don't wait to make it yours! Going once, twice...
